programme.desc: (S1E6) A violent power struggle erupts between Falcón and Rafa. As Félix finds a footing in the cocaine business, the DEA tries to lure him into the U.S.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E7) María implores Félix to move back to Sinaloa. Kiki gathers evidence of the Guadalajara cartel's pot fields. Neto Mourns.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E8) After the DEA closes in on Rafa's enormous pot field, Félix tries to stop his associates from retaliating. Kiki and Jaime meet with investigators.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E9) A desperate Jaime is stymied by bureaucratic paperwork. Mika worries about her husband. Félix urges Rafa to disappear.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E10) As pressure mounts, Félix returns to Sinaloa. An enraged Jaime and Mika seek justice and answers.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E1) Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E2) Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E3) Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar's political ambitions by proving he's narco.
